#include<stdio.h>

int main()
{
 long long int start,end,a,b,c;
 int counter=0;

 while(1)
 {
  counter=0;
  a=1;
  b=2;
  scanf("%lld %lld",&start,&end);
  if(start ==0 && end ==0)
   break;

  while(1)
  {
   c=a+b;
   a=b;
   b=c;
   if(c>=start && c<=end)
	counter++;
   if(c>=end)
  	break;
  }
  printf("%d\n",counter);
 }
 return 0;
}
